# ForceAwareACT

ForceAwareACT is a Python project skeleton for a contact-dynamics-aware vision-force ACT policy for contact-rich manipulation.

The implementation design and staged requirements are documented in [docs/contact_dynamics_force_act_design.md](docs/contact_dynamics_force_act_design.md).
